{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Alleluja.\n1. Slawejeet ta KUNGA\nWahrdn/ Slawejeet juhs\nKalpi ta KUNGA.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "2. Kas juhs stahwat ta\nKUNGA Naunmâ/ eekſch muh-\nsu Deewa Nauma Pagalneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "3. Slawejeet to KUNGU/ jo\ntas KUNGS irr labs/ dseedait\nwinna Wahrdam/ jo winſch irr\nmihtigs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "4. Jo tas KUNGS irr few\nJehkabu iswehlejs/ Israëlu par\nfawn Mantu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "5. Jo es finnu/ ka tas KUNGS\nleets irr/ un muhſu Kungs lee-\nlaks/ ne ka winſi Deewi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Wiſs/ kas tani KUNgam\ngribbahs/ to darra wiſsch/ Deb-\nbeſis/ un wirs Semmes/Juhra/\nun wiſſos Dſiktumos.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Kas tahs Padebbeſis us-\nwedd no Semmes Galleem/kas\nSibbinus darra ar Leetu / kas\nto Webju no fawahm apſlehyp-\ntahm Weetahm iswehd.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Kas Egiptes Birmdsim-\nnutchuſ kawe / no Zilwekeem\nlihs Lohpecm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Kas Sihnes un Brihu-\nmus fuhtija tavá Widdú Egip-\ntes-Semme/ prett Warāu un\nwiſſeem winna Kalpeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Kas dauds Tautas kawe/\nun nokawe warrenus Kehnians.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Stonu to Amoriteru\nKehnizu/ un Ogu to Kehnizu no\nBabsana/ un wiſſas Kanāāna\nWalstibus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Un deewe winnu Semini\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "par Eemantochanu/ par Eem\ntochanu faween Israëka &\ndium.\n13. KUNGS/ taws Wah\npaleek muhſchigt/ KUNGS/\nwa Peeminneſchana paleek\nRaddu Radveem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Jo tas KUNGS teefs\nfawus Landis / un tam bu\nſchehl pahr faween Kalpeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. To Pagann Elfi\nSudrabs un Selts / Zilwe\nRohku Darbs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Teem irr Mutte/ bet\nne runna/ teem irr Azzis bet\nne reds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Teem irr Aufis/ bet t\nne dfird/ ir ne kahda Dwafch\nirr winnu Mutte.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Kas tohs darra/ irr t\npatt ka winni/ ir wiſs/ kas u\nteem pataujahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Juhs no Israëka Nam\nma teizeet to KUNGU/ juhs n\nAāreza Nauna/ teizeet t\nKUNGU.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Juhs no Lewja Nauna\nteizeet to KUNGU/ kas juhs to\nKUNGU bibſteetees/ teizeet to\nKUNGU.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Slawehts lai irr tas\nKUNGS no Zianas / kas Je-\nrusaleme dſihwo/ Alleluja.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
